```plantuml
@startuml
title OAuth2 Authorization Code Grant Workflow\n**with SAML2 Post Binding for user provisioning**

box "HealthSphere" #LightBlue
participant "Apigee Edge" as AE #Orange
participant "Orion Health Platform" as OHP #Orange
end box

participant "HealthCloud" as HC #Green
participant "Embedded Browser" as EB #Green

HC -> EB :
EB -> AE : GET /authorize?response_type=code
AE --> EB : 302 https://<b><redirect_url></b> (SAML OR token)

group SAML Authentication
EB -> AE : POST /oauth2/saml
AE -> OHP : POST /login-auth/saml?path=/actor/current
OHP -> OHP : Verify SAMLResponse
OHP --> AE
AE -> AE : Generate authorization code
AE --> EB : 302 https://<b><redirect_url></b>?code=<code>
end

HC -> AE : POST /token?code=<code>
AE --> HC : 200 access_token + refresh_token

@enduml
```